reviewText: I love a good trailer disc... and this is nothing like a good trailer disc.  The trailers are faded, washed out and have horrible contrast.  Almost unwatchable.  The disc runs less than an hour too.  Save your money.
A waste of time and money A bunch movie trailers and no movies it could of been much better.

Bunch of washed out previews and some vhs edit rainbows point to low quality
for trailers available elswhere that are much better in quality.
Good try but no prize for this company.
